text: "T.N.T." is a 1976 song by Australian hard rock band AC/DC. It was taken from their second studio album of the same name. It went to number 19 in Australia. It was covered by American heavy metal band Anthrax in 2013. Category:1976 songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:AC/DC songs Category:Anthrax (band) songs
title: T.N.T. (song)
